msgid "traffic_ctl storage"
msgstr ""

# 69844f7e352c49ea8c813d0622e4dbea
#: ../../appendices/command-line/traffic_ctl.en.rst:227
msgid ""
"Mark a cache storage device as offline. The storage is identified by a "
"*path* which must match exactly a path specified in "
":file:`storage.config`. This removes the storage from the cache and "
"redirects requests that would have used this storage to other storage. "
"This has exactly the same effect as a disk failure for that storage. This"
" does not persist across restarts of the :program:`traffic_server` "
"process."
msgstr ""

